attributes.review: This app greeted me with a login page. I thought I was just going to be able to browse through it without giving up my precious email and password information. Honestly an app like this I would never trust it to safely keep my passwords and other information of mine.

attributes.title: ✨Wow✨
attributes.review:
I really was expecting a ✊GREAT✊app from our GREAT 🍊 president but it took 💯 days to download🙀I couldn’t believe my 👀eyes. But that’s okay. Because if he put this much time into making an app, surely he puts at least this much time into making America decent🥰When I opened this app I had to give my info😏 so of course I obliged😩. AND he asked me to vote for him. So of course after I was done working my 20 hours for the day(love our taxes😍😚) in the middle of desert 🌵 catching 🐍 snakes I would vote. I found lots of snakes 🐍. I love my job🥵, I personally bring them to the president 🍊 so they can be his friends👵🏻They are all albinos and they are called “Karen’s” they are so common 👴🏻and fun to find🤯🦎. All was well until…A SNAKE BIT ME 🦷 I was poisoned🦠so I quickly went to the hospital🏥 BUT apparently I couldn’t afford it 📈💰our dear president left me to pay for something that wasn’t my fault⁉️my heart was racing 🏃🏻‍♀️ 🗯 because of sadness🤧😱☹️and because I was dying😷 ⚰️ If only I didn’t have to pay for my own health😵
Don’t download unless you wanna die!
